title: #73: Love Scam (Sarah Tiana)
itunes:title: Love Scam with Sarah Tiana
description: Sarah Tiana met me at the Comedy Store to talk about her crazy experience with love in the Middle East. It's sort of a sad story. We're comics, so it was still funny, but it was still really sad at the same time. So it averages out to sort of sad.
